Annotation Type FormField


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface FormField

    • Element Detail

      • type

        public abstract FieldType type
        (Optional) The type of the FormField. Defaults to the text. Possible Values : select, checkbox, textarea, search, hidden
        Default:
        com.rikdata.ppl.common.form.FieldType.text

      • formFieldHierarchy

        public abstract FormFieldHierarchy formFieldHierarchy
        (Optional) The type of the FormField. Defaults to the text. Possible Values : select, checkbox, textarea, search, hidden
        Default:
        com.rikdata.ppl.common.form.FormFieldHierarchy.None

      • oneTimeUpdate

        public abstract boolean oneTimeUpdate
        (Optional) OneTimeUpdate fields are allowed to be entered for new records disabled for existing records in the form and ignored in the save method
        Default:
        false

      • readOnly

        public abstract boolean readOnly
        (Optional) read only fields are always present as read only in the form and user entered values ignore during save
        Default:
        false

      • required

        public abstract boolean required
        (Optional) required fields are shown as mandatory. Any nullable field in the database can be shown as required
        Default:
        false

      • nonprintable

        public abstract boolean nonprintable
        (Optional) fileds that ignore by print program
        Default:
        false

      • hiddenInList

        public abstract boolean hiddenInList
        (Optional) Fields not shown on list or search result page. Ex: Text Areas, Password, Audit Details
        Default:
        false

      • hiddenInForm

        public abstract boolean hiddenInForm
        (Optional) Fields not shown on web pages. Ex: Document Title, VersionUID
        Default:
        false

      • length

        public abstract int length
        (Optional) The field length. Used only for CSS purpose. The user entry is controlled by @Colum length
        Default:
        50

      • fieldGroup

        public abstract java.lang.String fieldGroup
        (Optional) The group name of the fields. All fields under the same group are shown together ex: in a single tab
        Default:
        "basic"

      • rows

        public abstract int rows
        Default:
        10

      • requiredInSearch

        public abstract boolean requiredInSearch
        (Optional) Field that makes an attribute mandatory for search. Ex: Opertaing Unit in Invoice, Sales Order Search
        Default:
        false

      • lovName

        public abstract java.lang.String lovName
        (Optional) List of value name that contains the values of this field. The corresponding method must be registered in common LOV Service
        Default:
        ""

      • fieldLabel

        public abstract java.lang.String fieldLabel
        (Optional) Field label. If entered system will use this value in web forms
        Default:
        ""

      • referencedLovName

        public abstract java.lang.String referencedLovName
        (Optional) lovName field provides List of value name that contains the values on that field. However, if the list of value needs to be dynamically generated then lovName cant be used referencedLovName finds the indepedent field name and corresponding value. Use that value to derive the lov values The corresponding method must be registered in common LOV Service
        Default:
        ""

      • referencedLovValue

        public abstract java.lang.String referencedLovValue
        (Optional) lovName field provides List of value name that contains the values on that field. However, if the list of value needs to be dynamically generated then lovName cant be used referencedLovValue finds the indepedent field name and corresponding value. Converts the value to a comma separated array and use it for select The corresponding method must be registered in common LOV Service
        Default:
        ""

      • displayType

        public abstract java.lang.String displayType
        (Optional) Detemines the way the field will be displayed in pages. Values : Dashboard, Table Default value ""
        Default:
        ""

      • cssClass

        public abstract java.lang.String cssClass
        (Optional) The field css class. Used only for CSS purpose.
        Default:
        ""

      • controlledBy

        public abstract java.lang.String controlledBy
        (Optional) List of comma seperated fields that control the value of this field. The value is shown as attr-controlled by in front end. Required for autoComplete fields In case of button fields, controlledBy values are passed to the server via GET request
        Default:
        ""

      • controls

        public abstract java.lang.String controls
        (Optional) List of comma seperated fields those are controlled by this value. The value is shown as attr-controls by in front end. The controlled field values defaults to null/blank on change of control field. In case of button fields, control objects are shown in a modal
        Default:
        ""
